import React from 'react'; import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Card, CardContent, CardDescription, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '../components/ui/card'; import { Button } from '../components/ui/button'; import { Users, CreditCard, TrendingUp, Activity, Plus, Eye } from 'lucide-react'; import useAuthStore from '../store/authStore'; import { subscriptionAPI, affiliateAPI, nutritionAPI } from '../lib/api'; const Dashboard = () => { const { user, isDoctor } = useAuthStore(); // Fetch subscription status const { data: subscriptionStatus } = useQuery({ queryKey: ['subscription-status'], queryFn: subscriptionAPI.getStatus, enabled: !!user, }); // Fetch affiliate stats for doctors const { data: affiliateStats } = useQuery({ queryKey: ['affiliate-stats'], queryFn: affiliateAPI.getStats, enabled: isDoctor() && !!user, }); // Fetch nutrition plans const { data: nutritionPlans } = useQuery({ queryKey: ['nutrition-plans'], queryFn: nutritionAPI.getPlans, enabled: !!user, }); const DoctorDashboard = () => (
{/* Subscription Status */} Subscription Status {subscriptionStatus?.is_active ? (

Active Subscription

Plan: {subscriptionStatus.plan_name}

Next billing: {new Date(subscriptionStatus.current_period_end).toLocaleDateString()}

) : (

No Active Subscription

Subscribe to access all features

)} {/* Stats Grid */}
Total Patients
{nutritionPlans?.length || 0}

Active nutrition plans

Referral Earnings
${affiliateStats?.total_earnings?.toFixed(2) || '0.00'}

Total commission earned

Referrals
{affiliateStats?.total_referrals || 0}

People referred

{/* Quick Actions */} Quick Actions Common tasks and features
); const PatientDashboard = () => (
{/* Welcome Card */} Welcome, {user?.first_name}! Track your nutrition journey and health goals

Your Health Dashboard

Monitor your progress and nutrition plans

{/* Nutrition Plans */} My Nutrition Plans View and manage your personalized nutrition plans {nutritionPlans?.length > 0 ? (
{nutritionPlans.slice(0, 3).map((plan) => (

{plan.name || 'Nutrition Plan'}

Created: {new Date(plan.created_at).toLocaleDateString()}

))}
) : (

No nutrition plans yet

)}
); return (

Dashboard

{isDoctor() ? 'Manage your practice and track your success' : 'Track your health and nutrition journey'}

{isDoctor() ? : }
); }; export default Dashboard;
